%3A+Move+To+Control+His+Writing+Cause+Him+to+Leave+Party&amp;rft.aufirst=C.+P.&amp;rft.aulast=Trussell&amp;rft.au=Trussell%2C+C.+P.&amp;rft.date=24+May+1951&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fgraphics8.nytimes.com%2Fpackages%2Fpdf%2Ftopics%2FSchulberg%2F1951-05-24-Schulberg-Tells.pdf&amp;rft.jtitle=The+New+York+Times&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
